OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA dry and sunny day for most.
OL,6,FCloudier across Northern Ireland and
OL,7,Fwestern Scotland, with the risk of
OL,8,Fsome rain here during the afternoon.
OL,9,FBreezy around some coasts, but for
OL,10,Fmany temperatures will be well above
OL,11,Fthe early April average.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FOutbreaks of rain will
OL,14,Fcontinue across western and some
OL,15,Fnorthern parts of Scotland. Otherwise,
OL,16,Fit is dry elsewhere with clear spells.
OL,17,FA few fog patches forming across
OL,18,Fsouthern England.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
