OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FPlenty of very warm
OL,6,Fsunshine once again across much of
OL,7,FEngland and Wales, with temperatures
OL,8,Fwell above average. Mostly dry for
OL,9,FNorthern Ireland and Scotland though
OL,10,Fgenerally cloudier here.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
